Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:11.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,到處是泡泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,唉 頭髮 硬梆梆的
