Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,萬里 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要沒水了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:32.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不會吧
